'''''Megalomphalus margaritae''''' is a [[species]] of very small [[sea snail]], a [[marine (ocean)|marine]] [[gastropod]] [[mollusk]] in the [[family (biology)|family]] [[Vanikoridae]].<ref name="WoRMS">{{WRMS species|419717|''Megalomphalus margaritae'' Rol<U+00E1>n & Rubio, 1998|||WoRMS (2010). Megalomphalus margaritae Rol<U+00E1>n & Rubio, 1998. Accessed through:  [[World Register of Marine Species]] at <nowiki>http://www.marinespecies.eu/aphia.php?p=taxdetails&id=419717</nowiki> on 14 August 2010}}</ref>

